title: Add Metric Targets to Prometheus
tags: @zettel _method prometheus
roam-id: d62093bb-ef63-44f0-a98d-7e3c744b7eba
type: text/markdown

use the following under `scrape_configs:`

``` yaml
- job_name: "kafka_exporter"
  static_configs:
    - targets: ["mobilelgniter:9308"]
```

here is a complete example:

``` yaml
global:
  scrape_interval: 15s
scrape_configs:
  - job_name: "kafka_exporter"
    static_configs:
      - targets: ["mobilelgniter:9308"]
```
